node.text:
The harder the battle, the sweeter the victory 👑 

For the @pho3nixife Sub8 Project, I will face many battles.
The battle with history,
The battle with my limits,
And the battle with my rival - @nicolaspirigofficial 

This is going to be a whole new push on what’s possible but I am ready to take on the battle and prove what I can do 🥇

#DefyTheImpossible  #Pho3nix  #Sub7Sub8  #Triathlon 
🎬 @mana.studios  @orbitalstud.io |

Hands up if you’re ready to watch our new video! 🙌

A week on from the inaugural @thecollinscuptri and still buzzing about how this event is going to change the future of triathlon! 

🔗: Hit the link in my bio to give my race recap a watch!
📸: @professionaltriathletesorg 

#thecollinscup #teameurope #triathlonlife #newvideoalert #weekendvibes #raceday #learnfromthepros #trichicks #dreambig #livetoinspire #headtohead #livetorace #challengeyourself #gohard #battlebraids #teamcharlesbarclay

Happy Friday😄

Vegas baby✌🏻
A little pit stop on our road trip yesterday, had to be done!🚙 And yes I’m wearing a turtle neck jumper in 38degree heat🤪
465miles🛣
6 suitcases🧳
3 bikes🚲 
2 rental cars🚘 
1 storm⛈ 
$20 won on Roulette🎰 
ALL the snacks🍪🍰🍬🌮🍔🥞🍒
1 vlog coming soon🎥

node.text:
New week, same goals, stay focused!!👀 
On route to LAX for my next block of training with a little road trip leading into the 70.3 Worlds in St George, Utah.🏜 
Current focus is in on recovery, keeping healthy & getting ready to do my final preparations for Worlds! ✈️🌎💪🏻
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
#newweek #mondaymotivation #motivation #livetoinspire #worldchamps #roadtrip #bloodsweatanddata #wahooligan #rideon #AllTribesOneClan #rebornfaster #becube #GivesYouWings #OneObsession #FindFaster #girlpower #BattleBraids #TeamCharlesBarclay

node.text:
Huge congrats to Team Europe for winning the first ever Collins Cup, what a team effort from everyone🙌🏻🇪🇺🏆
I am so proud to be part of this inaugural event in which the @professionaltriathletesorg have put triathlon on the global stage that it so deserves!!🌎 
Unfortunately I felt unwell with stomach issues before the swim, couldn’t keep anything down throughout the bike & just did everything I could to finish strong for the team💪🏻
Absolutely gutted to miss the team celebrations with the winners trophy but I couldn’t be more proud of my team♥️🇪🇺
📸: @professionaltriathletesorg 
#thecollinscup #BattleforGlory #teameurope #winners #winnerwinnerchickendinner #GivesYouWings #livetoinspire #becubebefast #OneObsession #wahooligan #rebornfaster #strongwomen #BattleBraids #TeamCharlesBarclay

node.text:
Tomorrow we race the first ever Collins Cup here in Samorin, Slovakia🏆💪🏻
I’m ready to go ALL IN for Team Europe!🇪🇺
You can watch the action live from 1pm local time/ 12pm U.K. time👀
The first match of 3 athletes sets off at 1pm with matches starting every 10mins thereafter💥
To find out how to watch hit the link in my bio & head to ‘PTO LIVE’, you’re not going to want to me this!🔥
📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
🏆: @thecollinscuptri 
📍: @xbionicsphere

node.text:
Oh hi 👀 it’s me again! 

I’ve always dreamt of having a pink bike, and the day has finally come! 

A huge thank you to @cube.bikes for making this happen & to @enduraofficial for the matching custom kit! 

Check out our latest video on YouTube to see this bad boy in action & get some more updates on our training camp at @clublasanta 🏝 

🚲 @cube.bikes have also made a video about the process of creating my custom #cubelitening so be sure to give that a watch too! 

🔗 Link to both are in my bio!

📸: @hollycharlesphotography_ 
#newbikeday #prettyinpink #bestdayever #bikeporn #bikegoals #traininstyle #lookgoodfeelgood #womeninsport #kitgoals #bikerchick #cyclelife #qom #quadsquad #bikelife #goneriding #cyclingculture #cyclefashion #trichicks #girlpower #teamcharlesbarclay
